title: Our Happy Ending (Hotel Del Luna OST)
lyrics: Tone . Tone IU là D, Capo 2 chơi C uriui gyeolmari seulpeuji anhasseumyeon johgesseo i sunga neul tteoolli myeo ulji anhdo rok geu reo myeon an doelkka One Happy Ending geu reol su eobsdamyeon aju apeun sangcheoga doeeojwo neoreul gi eokhal su iss neun hyungi jido rok gi kkeo i apeulge geuraeju gessni yeon ya khan neoreul barabo myeo oraen goeroumeul jamsi i jeo idae ro hanbeon deo nege angyeo swi go si peo jakku keo jineun duryeoumbo da chameul su eobsneun yok simi na nuni bu sil gyeo urui neo do bogo sipeojyeo geu reol su eobsdamyeon i jangmyeoneuro nal gi eokhaejwo seogeulpeu ge areumda un uriui bam do kko chi pi narineun Our Happy Ending
